327
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:38,300
 The fan depicts a house from the Jiang Residence. 

328
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:41,499
 Both sides should have equal structure and uniform layout. 

329
00:36:41,499 --> 00:36:45,780
 But the west courtyard has a window, while the east becomes a wall. 

330
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:48,860
 The stone foundation underneath is also somewhat different. 

331
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:52,839
 I'm afraid there might be a secret chamber hidden underneath this wall. 

332
00:36:54,939 --> 00:36:58,839
 Please allow me to investigate the Jiang Residence. 

333
00:37:02,060 --> 00:37:05,380
Vice Minister Liu it has two doors and four windows like the west courtyard.

334
